{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"342334-plants-are-everywhere","title":"Plants Are Everywhere","description":"Plants grow everywhere — on high mountains, on arid lands, and even under the sea. Explore different types of plants in this book.","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"3","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Ritu Desai"],"illustrators":["Ekta Bharti"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Pratham Books","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/342334-plants-are-everywhere"},"cover":{"card":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/434073/size3/3927b068f2f1009ae79ef445c56eb5be.jpg","large":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/434073/size6/3927b068f2f1009ae79ef445c56eb5be.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/432379/size6/3cc97e3cf798686ba1591e41179d6ad3.jpg","text":"Plants grow everywhere —\non high mountains,\non arid lands,","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/432380/size6/4fe078af4f4c2c95d7aa9f58a4170f17.jpg","text":"and even under the sea.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/432381/size6/d46bd1bce2c48c0172692bc06557cd9b.jpg","text":"Plants grow in\nscorching heat\nand shivering cold.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/432383/size6/ccc7f17f4719053ad46284bb4bf26722.jpg","text":"Plants climb.\nCucumber and\ngrape vines lean\non and climb\nup poles and\nbranches.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/432385/size6/231f92192266c588ab5d0b50dc2e9d96.jpg","text":"Plants creep.\nPumpkin and watermelon\ncreepers glide along the ground.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/432386/size6/3e3b14ad3f4594b48a003144bec289c7.jpg","text":"Plants grow on water.\nWater lilies and lotuses float on\nthe surface of lakes and ponds.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/432388/size6/b21ad3fe8c120d09ace22dfab31a3ce5.jpg","text":"Plants grow under water.\nSwaying seagrass are rooted\nto the bottom of the sea.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/432389/size6/aef66c654b2a8698a038a37ce930e6dd.jpg","text":"Plants bloom in the harshest of winters.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/432390/size6/63649a49c6b1e8ccccc4c36068e116d7.jpg","text":"Cabbages and collards\ngrow hidden under a\nblanket of snow.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/432392/size6/4ea1e9a6a989c1670dcdab860de55989.jpg","text":"Plants grow in the hottest of summers.\nCacti bloom in sandy deserts, with their\nshallow roots growing beneath the surface.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/432393/size6/2f57cf5c94684818e63a3a887b5b4aaf.jpg","text":"Plants grow on rocks and stone.","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/432396/size6/67c6a4bc5fb983457e41f3a115537ebd.jpg","text":"Slippery moss spreads like a velvety green\nblanket on riverside rocks and damp caves.","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/432397/size6/da25a60d9cfb5703dc893ed5061638f1.jpg","text":"Plants grow\nunder the soil.\nPotatoes and carrots grow under\nthe ground, with only their leaves\npeeking above the earth.","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/432400/size6/a171ee6f8bb2ea2967f4a59460e3cb90.jpg","text":"Plants emerge from the soil and grow taller and taller. They stretch and reach\nout for the sun,\nlike all of us.","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":14,"words":176}}